Not the 4kids version. In this season the Winx meet Layla, a fairy who is trying to save the pixies from Darkar. Bloom, Stella, Sky, Brandon, and Layla save the pixies. The Trix are back again and team up with Darkar to beat the winx. Darkar kidnapped Bloom and makes her part of the dark side where she doesn't know her friends. At the end sky saves Bloom and the Winx defeat Darkar.
good fun dvd but the intro song is diffrent
My daughter loves her Winx Club!

My family are big fans of the Winx club series I just wish it was easier to find seasons 3+ in volumes or other wise I prefer not to pay for the digital copies. On the plus side Amazon Prime allows you to watch all of them. The chronological order is: Winx Club seasons 1-3 (Note: season 3 is also Enchantix) or Winx Club Specials. Winx club: The Secret of the Lost Kingdom (1st movie). Winx Club Magical Adventure (2nd movie). Winx Club: Believix. Winx Club: Beyond Believix. Winx Club: The Mystery of the Abyss (3rd movie). Winx Club: Bloomix is the new season. They also have a spin off series called PopPixie it is about the pixies in pixie village (can be watched at any point after season 3).
